Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.14,0:23:06.92,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そっと土に埋めたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.02,0:23:13.28,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}A flower blooming in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:18.80,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}その日を夢見て…
